OL,3,C'It's disgusting': Families being
OL,4,C'plagued' by flies from local sewage
OL,5,Cworks
OL,7,FLocal resident Kelly Long said: "You
OL,8,Fcould have the window open for a small
OL,9,Famount of time with the lamp on and
OL,10,Fnext thing the wall is covered with
OL,11,Flittle black flies.
OL,13,F"It's not hygienic, it's disgusting
OL,14,Fwhen they land in anything you drink
OL,15,Fand eat."
OL,17,FThe water company also says it does
OL,18,Fwhat it can to control them, but there
OL,19,Fare strict regulations on the
OL,20,Fchemicals it can use.
