OL,3,C'It's disgusting': Families being
OL,4,C'plagued' by flies from local sewage
OL,5,Cworks
OL,7,FJohn Penicud, from Southern Water,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The flies are harmless, they're
OL,9,Fattracted to areas of stagnant water
OL,10,Flike naturally in the environment.
OL,12,F"At our Uckfield treatment works we
OL,13,Fhave large areas of stagnant water so
OL,14,Fit's a natural process and the flies
OL,15,Fare just in their natural habitat.
