OL,7,F"Obviously that's not acceptable to
OL,8,Fthe residents locally and that's why
OL,9,Fwe control them with insecticides
OL,10,Fwhich are licensed to us by the
OL,11,FEnvironment Agency and we use them
OL,12,Funder the guidances of industry
OL,13,Fleading experts that we've engaged to
OL,14,Fhelp us manage the problem at
OL,15,FUckfield."
