OL,5,Cworks
OL,7,FWealden District Council says the land
OL,8,Fsouth of the sewage works was given
OL,9,Fplanning permission for new homes
OL,10,Feight years ago and it shares the
OL,11,Fconcerns of local residents about the
OL,12,Fflies.
OL,14,FThe council told ITV News Meridian:
OL,15,F"It is Southern Water that are
OL,16,Fresponsible to ensure the efficient
OL,17,Frunning of their plant and limiting
OL,18,Fany flies originating from the works.
